content_html: Gulmi, Sept 18: The Kaligandaki Corridor and Madan Bhandari Highway blocked for traffic due to landslides triggered by continuous rain have come into operation. The Kaligandaki corridor was completely blocked since Wednesday morning after a landslide at Rakse in Kaligandaki Rural Municipality-2 under the Gulmi sectio
